version_description: Not 100 percent sure about the song parts.
Capo 3 - Easy chords version, no barres.

This version is based on an acoustic cover I found on Youtube (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2NAxtLan4YY). Most of the song should be played with a fast strumming pattern, listen to the original song to determine the pattern.
I copied these chords from elle me dit, emily is the english version.
The chords are also very easy to play on ukulele.
